      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blackwood%2C_New_Jersey"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "The community features Blackwood Lake and the nearby Farrows Run stream, adding natural charm to the area.",
